{"title":"新月","date":"2021-04-22T09:48:52.000Z","date_formatted":{"ll":"Apr 22, 2021","L":"04/22/2021","MM-DD":"04-22"},"author":"白桦","link":"2021/04/22/Crescent","comments":true,"tags":["诗"],"categories":["诗"],"updated":"2021-04-22T09:55:45.617Z","content":"<p>锐利的弦月<br>\n被薄云萦绕<br>\n冷峻的面庞平添了些<br>\n本不该有的柔情</p>\n<p>他说：<br>\n明天就是新月<br>\n没有光<br>\n我们都不复存在</p>\n<p>夜，没有答案的夜<br>\n还是一如既往的沉默</p>\n<p>溪水在鹅卵石上拍打着<br>\n激起一片水雾<br>\n清爽、温柔<br>\n且闪耀着白光</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>*注：天文学的新月（朔），有时也称为“<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E9%BB%91%E6%9C%88\" target=\"_blank\">黑月</a>”以免造成混淆，从定义看是发生在太阳和月球有着相同<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E9%BB%83%E7%B6%93\" target=\"_blank\">黄经</a>的<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E5%90%88_(%E5%A4%A9%E9%AB%94%E4%BD%8D%E7%BD%AE)\" target=\"_blank\">合</a>，这时从地球上是看不见月球的。</p>\n</blockquote>\n","prev":{"title":"藏匿于人海中的杂音——精神分裂者数描","link":"2021/05/18/Schizophrenia"},"next":{"title":"雪松","link":"2021/03/25/Cedar"},"plink":"http://wardzhou.art/2021/04/22/Crescent/","reward":true,"copyright":{"author":"白桦","license":"Attribution-NonCommercial-NoDerivatives 4.0 International(<a href=\"https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc-nd/4.0/\" rel=\\\"external nofollow\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\">CC BY-NC-ND 4.0</a>)","updated":"April 22, 2021"},"reading_time":"141 words in 1 min"}